## Enumeration Members

|  Member | Value | Description |
|  --- | --- | --- |
|  InventorySupply | <code>&quot;InventorySupply&quot;</code> | Role tells that this channel can be used to track inventory entries.Channels with this role can be treated as warehouses |
|  OrderExport | <code>&quot;OrderExport&quot;</code> | Role tells that this channel can be used to track order export activities. |
|  OrderImport | <code>&quot;OrderImport&quot;</code> | Role tells that this channel can be used to track order import activities. |
|  Primary | <code>&quot;Primary&quot;</code> | This role can be combined with some other roles (e.g. with <code>InventorySupply</code>) to represent the fact that this particular channel is the primary/master channel among the channels of the same type. |
|  ProductDistribution | <code>&quot;ProductDistribution&quot;</code> | Role tells that this channel can be used to expose products to a specific distribution channel. It can be used by the cart to select a product price. |
